==事故与意外==
*2004年11月30日，{{link-en|獅子航空538號班機|Lion Air Flight 538}}，一架[[麥道MD-82|麥道MD-82]]客机坠毁在[[梭罗_(印尼)|梭罗]]，25人死亡。<ref name="Lion Air Accident 2004">{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2011/11/18/indonesias-lion-air-rises-obscurity.html |title=Accident: Fatal Accident in 2004 |work=The Jakarta Post |accessdate=22 November 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120181457/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2011/11/18/indonesias-lion-air-rises-obscurity.html |archivedate=20 November 2011 |df= }}</ref>
*2013年4月13日，一架[[波音737|波音737]]客機於[[峇里|峇里]][[登巴薩|登巴薩]][[伍拉·賴國際機場|伍拉·賴國際機場]]準備降落時墮海，造成45人受傷。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=613363&csid=261_367 |title=印尼廉航客機降落峇里時墜海增至45人傷 |work=商業電台 |date=2013-04-13 |accessdate=2013-04-14 |archive-date=2019-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203111916/https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=613363&csid=261_367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2018年10月29日，一架執行[[獅子航空610號班機空難|獅子航空610號班機]]的波音737 MAX 8客机，預定上午從[[雅加達|雅加達]]的[[蘇加諾-哈達國際機場|蘇加諾-哈達國際機場]]飛往[[邦加島|邦加島]]的[[邦加檳港|邦加檳港]]，不料在起飛13分鐘後於[[加拉璜|加拉璜]]海面墜毀，機上載有189人，全部遇難。<ref>{{cite web |author=Agustinus Beo Da Costa, Cindy Silviana |url=https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-indonesia-crash/indonesia-says-lion-air-passenger-flight-crashes-off-sumatra-idUKKCN1N306R |title=Indonesian plane with 189 aboard crashes into sea near Jakarta, feared sunk |publisher=Reuters |access-date=2018-10-29 |archive-date=2019-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820091232/https://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-indonesia-crash/indonesia-says-lion-air-passenger-flight-crashes-off-sumatra-idUKKCN1N306R |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-46035609 |title=Lion Air crash: Indonesia to inspect Boeing 737-Max 8 planes |date=2018-10-30 |work=BBC |accessdate=2018-11-28 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124022656/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-46035609 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

